column16: Curt Casali pops out to first baseman Justin Smoak.
Desmond Jennings doubles (3) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Kevin Pillar.   Evan Longoria scores.    Steven Souza Jr.
Steven Souza Jr.   singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Michael Saunders.   Evan Longoria to 2nd.
Steve Pearce flies out to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Taylor Motter flies out to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Brandon Guyer pops out to first baseman Justin Smoak.
Kevin Kiermaier singles on a soft ground ball to pitcher Dustin Antolin.
Curt Casali homers (5) on a fly ball to left field.   Steve Pearce scores.    Steven Souza Jr.
Desmond Jennings lines out sharply to third baseman Josh Donaldson.
